---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import ProcessSteps from '../components/ProcessSteps.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Steam Cleaning Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional car steam cleaning in Fort Lauderdale. Mobile service - we come to you! Kills bacteria, mold, and allergens without chemicals. Same-day appointments. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}upholstery-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Upholstery Cleaning Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Steam Cleaning Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional steam cleaning sanitizes your car's interior using high-temperature vapor that kills bacteria, mold, and allergens without chemicals."
  currentPage="/steam-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Steam cleaning is the deepest clean you can give a car interior. Water heated above 200°F produces vapor that penetrates surfaces, kills microorganisms on contact, and loosens grime that other methods leave behind. No chemicals needed—just pure, hot steam.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We bring our steam cleaning service directly to your home or office anywhere in Fort Lauderdale. From waterfront homes in Rio Vista to condos near Flagler Village, we come to you with commercial steam equipment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          In Florida's humid climate, mold and mildew thrive inside vehicles. Steam cleaning kills these organisms at the source rather than just masking the smell with air fresheners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does Steam Cleaning Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Steam cleaning in Fort Lauderdale costs $75 to $150 depending on your vehicle size and how thorough you want us to be.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          A basic steam cleaning covers seats, carpets, and main surfaces. Full interior steam cleaning adds door panels, headliner, vents, and every crevice in the cabin. Larger vehicles with more surface area cost more.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We'll discuss your needs and give you an exact price before starting.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does Steam Cleaning Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Steam cleaning takes about 45 minutes for most vehicles, with surfaces drying within 1-2 hours.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Steam cleaning actually uses very little water compared to shampooing. The high temperature means moisture evaporates quickly, so your car dries faster. This also makes steam cleaning safe for electronics, screens, and areas where you don't want excess water.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Your car is ready to drive immediately after we finish, though surfaces may feel slightly damp for an hour or so.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Why Choose Steam Cleaning for Your Car?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Steam kills 99% of bacteria, mold, and allergens without leaving chemical residue behind. It's the safest deep-clean option for your interior.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Fort Lauderdale's humidity creates perfect conditions for mold and mildew growth inside vehicles. Air conditioning systems pull in moisture. Wet shoes and swimsuits introduce water. Spills that don't dry completely become breeding grounds.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Steam cleaning addresses problems that other methods can't:</p>
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-1">Kills mold and mildew</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">High temperature destroys organisms on contact, not just on the surface but deep in materials.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-1">Eliminates allergens</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dust mites, pollen, and pet dander get neutralized by the heat.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-1">Removes odors at the source</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Steam penetrates where smells originate rather than covering them up.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-1">Chemical-free</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Safe for people with sensitivities, children, and pets. Nothing but water.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-1">Sanitizes hard surfaces</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Steering wheels, shifters, and buttons get truly clean, not just wiped.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Signs steam cleaning would help:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Musty or mildew smell in your car</li>
          <li>Allergies act up when driving</li>
          <li>Visible mold spots on surfaces</li>
          <li>You want the deepest possible clean</li>
          <li>Chemical sensitivities prevent using traditional products</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-6">Our Steam Cleaning Process</h2>
        <ProcessSteps steps={[
          { title: "Initial Vacuuming", description: "We remove loose debris first so steam can penetrate surfaces effectively." },
          { title: "Upholstery Steaming", description: "High-temperature vapor penetrates seat fabric and carpet fibers, killing bacteria and loosening embedded dirt." },
          { title: "Leather Surfaces", description: "Lower pressure steam safely cleans and sanitizes leather without damage." },
          { title: "Hard Surfaces", description: "Dashboard, door panels, console, and trim get steamed to remove grime and kill germs." },
          { title: "Detail Areas", description: "Vents, cup holders, buttons, and crevices get targeted steam cleaning." },
          { title: "Final Wipe", description: "We wipe down all surfaces to remove any loosened grime and moisture." }
        ]} />
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-2">Protect After Cleaning</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Steam cleaning can be combined with other services. Many clients follow up with fabric protection or leather conditioning to keep their freshly sanitized interior protected longer.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Steam Cleaning Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c9a227] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$75-$150 depending on scope</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">About 45 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Kills 99% of bacteria</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Chemical-free cleaning</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Dries in 1-2 hours</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Steam Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}odor-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Odor Removal</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}fabric-protection-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Fabric Protection</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}leather-conditioning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Leather Conditioning</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}full-detail-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Full Detail</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
